| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2878 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e7a3ada8-edb6-53fc-b845-47647b6a7eb8"
